// Adamomaton umbrella go.work — aggregates every Go module across all
// submodules so local dev resolves cross-component imports via paths
// instead of network module fetches.
//
// Phase 2 (scripts/migrate.sh) populates the `use` directives once each
// sub-repo holds real code. Until then this file is the empty workspace
// declaration that lets `go work sync` run from the umbrella root
// without complaint.
//
// Production builds (sub-repo CI without the umbrella) resolve
// dependencies via each go.mod's pinned tag.

go 1.25
